{"tid":1539290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"逆向思維，我地只要做多一年就會拎晒五大訴求","createTime":"2019-09-04T09:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:30.000Z","uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"246d0accbabcff06e3d4cad038ce51a0a95e05f6","tid":1539290,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"一個訴求平均用左三個月既時間<br />\n唔講任何因素，以最基本既慣性邏輯推論<br />\n4個訴求 X 3個月爭取時間=1年<br />\n<br />\n絕望既人，想尋死既人，請盡快打消念頭<br />\n我地行多一年就贏<br />\n繼續一齊行既人，接落黎既時間要一次比一次小心<br />\n計劃一次要比一次週密<br />\n被捕人數要一次比一次少<br />\n<br />\n香港人，辛苦啦！<br />\n一齊，繼續行落去。"},{"pid":"368faed2563c281532a07bf61f093a01b42d220e","tid":1539290,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭宣布撤回送中條例的六大陰謀</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n快啲同我入黎睇曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f672f0b7c5f0a7d34ba9147ada44f3028910a7a","tid":1539290,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}